{"tid":541984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方：劉頴匡,  陳國強, 姚松炎將被DQ","createTime":"2018-01-27T04:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T04:01:42.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4123e665f35cdc48565e5f26a016ad836f2d053b","tid":541984,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20180127/20180127112159lc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fhknews%2F20180127%2F20180127112159lc.html&d=nNyybF8Xdylwz8xFDQIOoghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=64953531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20180127/20180127112159lc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n立會補選：姚松炎短期內DQ　本土派亦凍過水 (11:21)<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=nNyybF8Xdylwz8xFDQIOoghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f33a42d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】已報名參加立法會香港島補選的香港眾志常委周庭，今天（27日）正式被選舉主任取消參選資格（DQ），消息指已報名參加九龍西補選的原建築界立法會議員姚松炎，亦會於極短期內獲通知被DQ。至於民主派的九西補選「Plan B（後備人選）」民主黨深水埗區議員袁海文，因民主黨一向反對港獨或自決公投，故相信他可過關成功參選。<br />\n<br />\n此外，由於政府已說明鼓吹「民主自決」違反《基本法》，估計最少2名本土派新東補選參選人劉頴匡及沙田區議員陳國強，亦極大機會會被DQ。至於代表民主派參選新東的新同盟前立法會議員范國威，雖然他身兼「香港本土」成員，但他從未主張港獨，消息指他亦可過關。<br />\n<br />\n已報名參選九西的還有民建聯深水埗區議員鄭泳舜及前民建聯成員蔡東洲。已報名參選新東的還有工聯會前立法會議員鄧家彪、西貢區議員方國珊、性傾向條例家校關注組成員趙佩玉、獨立人士陳玉娥，以及剛於今早報名的前民主黨立法會議員黃成智。"},{"pid":"39296a40c192f70540847f7b6f194309d8857147","tid":541984,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156a9c10110514f047c26dd6a2976702df36518a","tid":541984,"uid":120814,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"等緊睇dq佢要負咩政治後果 早兩日講到好大"},{"pid":"83ee5ed1c0753e2908146cd52a5996d9f1bfadff","tid":541984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新同盟前立法會議員范國威，雖然他身兼「香港本土」成員，但他從未主張港獨，消息指他亦可過關。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開心死佢啦！<br />\n<br />\n咁姚松炎都無提港獨喎, 又DQ？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a946e5c4d07f3e99931430fa3e0ce95cf94f7ef1","tid":541984,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"一早預咗<br />\n係有班人扮瞓<br />\n泛民有班人等獨享入閘權"},{"pid":"04c8430b99b066f5d75167c592dfcfa89f4d65a1","tid":541984,"uid":79563,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"156a9c10110514f047c26dd6a2976702df36518a","tid":541984,"uid":120814,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"等緊睇dq佢要負咩政治後果 早兩日講到好大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"主要係派出楊岳橋去紮營, 問你怕未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/25289591_1578416618918403_4750402780705646610_n.jpg?oh=3ad446f4106e44aca18ceabe3f46da01&amp;oe=5AF1B271\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F25289591_1578416618918403_4750402780705646610_n.jpg%3Foh%3D3ad446f4106e44aca18ceabe3f46da01%26oe%3D5AF1B271&h=14981ade&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87e995d81709375f41ee404930df26867fcf4a7f","tid":541984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a946e5c4d07f3e99931430fa3e0ce95cf94f7ef1","tid":541984,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"一早預咗<br />\n係有班人扮瞓<br />\n泛民有班人等獨享入閘權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"佢地依家都係等獨享入閘權"},{"pid":"c07a6cd01a4d2405075515f109903ef13fd66d24","tid":541984,"uid":73092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"83ee5ed1c0753e2908146cd52a5996d9f1bfadff","tid":541984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新同盟